<!DOCTYPE html>
<html lang="en">
<head>
    <meta charset="UTF-8">
    <meta name="viewport" content="width=device-width, initial-scale=1.0">
    <title>Construction Materials and Procurement - Benny Estimates</title>
    <script src="https://cdn.tailwindcss.com"></script>
    <link href="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/remixicon@4.2.0/fonts/remixicon.css" rel="stylesheet"/>
    <script>
        tailwind.config = {
            darkMode: 'class',
            theme: {
                extend: {
                    colors: {
                        primary: {
                            50: '#eff6ff',
                            100: '#dbeafe',
                            200: '#bfdbfe',
                            300: '#93c5fd',
                            400: '#60a5fa',
                            500: '#3b82f6',
                            600: '#2563eb',
                            700: '#1d4ed8',
                            800: '#1e40af',
                            900: '#1e3a8a',
                        }
                    },
                    animation: {
                        'fade-in': 'fadeIn 0.3s ease-in-out',
                        'slide-up': 'slideUp 0.3s ease-out',
                    },
                    keyframes: {
                        fadeIn: {
                            '0%': { opacity: '0' },
                            '100%': { opacity: '1' },
                        },
                        slideUp: {
                            '0%': { transform: 'translateY(20px)', opacity: '0' },
                            '100%': { transform: 'translateY(0)', opacity: '1' },
                        },
                    }
                }
            }
        }
    </script>
    <style>
        * {
            scrollbar-width: none;
            -ms-overflow-style: none;
            transition: background-color 0.3s ease, color 0.3s ease, border-color 0.3s ease;
        }
        *::-webkit-scrollbar {
            display: none;
        }
        .dark body {
            color-scheme: dark;
        }
        .material-card {
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }
        .material-card:hover {
            transform: translateY(-5px);
            box-shadow: 0 20px 25px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 10px 10px -5px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.04);
        }
        .theme-btn {
            backdrop-filter: blur(10px);
            box-shadow: 0 10px 15px -3px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.1), 0 4px 6px -2px rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.05);
        }

        /* Modal styles */
        .modal-overlay {
            position: fixed;
            top: 0;
            left: 0;
            right: 0;
            bottom: 0;
            background-color: rgba(0, 0, 0, 0.5);
            display: flex;
            align-items: center;
            justify-content: center;
            z-index: 1000;
            opacity: 0;
            visibility: hidden;
            transition: all 0.3s ease;
        }

        .modal-overlay.active {
            opacity: 1;
            visibility: visible;
        }

        .modal-content {
            background-color: white;
            border-radius: 1rem;
            padding: 2rem;
            max-width: 600px;
            width: 90%;
            max-height: 80vh;
            overflow-y: auto;
            transform: translateY(20px);
            transition: transform 0.3s ease;
        }

        .dark .modal-content {
            background-color: #1f2937;
            color: #f3f4f6;
        }

        .modal-overlay.active .modal-content {
            transform: translateY(0);
        }

        .modal-body {
            margin-top: 1rem;
            line-height: 1.6;
        }

        .modal-footer {
            margin-top: 2rem;
            padding-top: 1rem;
            border-top: 1px solid #e5e7eb;
        }

        .dark .modal-footer {
            border-top-color: #374151;
        }

        /* Responsive text adjustments */
        @media (max-width: 640px) {
            .hero-title {
                font-size: 2rem !important;
                line-height: 1.2 !important;
            }
            .material-card {
                padding: 1rem !important;
            }
        }

        /* Ensure buttons are clickable */
        button {
            cursor: pointer;
        }
    </style>
</head>
 <%- include('../header.ejs') %>
<body class="bg-gray-50 dark:bg-gray-900 text-gray-900 dark:text-gray-100 min-h-screen">
  
   

    <!-- Main Content -->
    <main class="container mx-auto px-4 py-8">
        <!-- Page Header -->
        <div class="text-center mb-12">
            <h1 class="hero-title text-4xl md:text-5xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 mb-4">
                Construction Materials & Procurement
            </h1>
            <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-lg max-w-3xl mx-auto">
                Complete guides on construction materials, costs, installation, and procurement strategies for successful projects
            </p>
        </div>

        <!-- Hero Image -->
        <div class="rounded-2xl overflow-hidden mb-12 shadow-2xl">
            <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1507136566006-cfc505b114fc?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=2070&q=80" 
                 alt="Construction Materials" 
                 class="w-full h-64 md:h-96 object-cover">
        </div>

        <!-- Materials Grid -->
        <div class="grid grid-cols-1 md:grid-cols-2 lg:grid-cols-3 gap-8 mb-12">
            <!-- Brick Masonry -->
            <article class="material-card bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1545324418-cc1a3fa10c00?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" 
                         alt="Brick Masonry" 
                         class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 hover:scale-110">
                </div>
                <div class="p-6">
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-red-100 dark:bg-red-900 text-red-800 dark:text-red-300 text-xs font-semibold rounded-full">
                            Masonry
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 mb-3">
                        Brick Masonry Guide – Types, Uses, Cost, & Benefits
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm mb-4">
                        Brick masonry is one of the most enduring and widely adopted construction methods in the world. From traditional housing to modern architectural facades, brick remains a popular choice due to its durability, aesthetic appeal, and thermal properties. Different types of bricks include clay bricks, concrete bricks, and engineering bricks, each suited for specific applications.
                    </p>
                    <button onclick="openModal(1)" class="inline-flex items-center text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 font-medium hover:text-primary-800 dark:hover:text-primary-300 text-sm cursor-pointer">
                        Read Guide <i class="ri-arrow-right-line ml-2"></i>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </article>

            <!-- Concrete Slab -->
            <article class="material-card bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1581094794329-c8112a89af12?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" 
                         alt="Concrete Slab" 
                         class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 hover:scale-110">
                </div>
                <div class="p-6">
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-gray-100 dark:bg-gray-700 text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-300 text-xs font-semibold rounded-full">
                            Concrete
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 mb-3">
                        How Much Does a Concrete Slab Cost?
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm mb-4">
                        Concrete slabs are foundational elements in residential and commercial construction, forming the base for patios, garages, sheds, and homes. The cost of a concrete slab depends on factors like thickness, reinforcement, site preparation, and local labor rates. On average, expect to pay between $4 and $8 per square foot for a standard 4-inch slab, with additional costs for finishing and curing.
                    </p>
                    <button onclick="openModal(2)" class="inline-flex items-center text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 font-medium hover:text-primary-800 dark:hover:text-primary-300 text-sm cursor-pointer">
                        Read Guide <i class="ri-arrow-right-line ml-2"></i>
                    </button>
                </div>
            </article>

            <!-- Metal Roof -->
            <article class="material-card bg-white dark:bg-gray-800 rounded-xl overflow-hidden shadow-lg border border-gray-200 dark:border-gray-700">
                <div class="h-48 overflow-hidden">
                    <img src="https://images.unsplash.com/photo-1541888946425-d81bb19240f5?ixlib=rb-4.0.3&auto=format&fit=crop&w=800&q=80" 
                         alt="Metal Roof Installation" 
                         class="w-full h-full object-cover transition-transform duration-500 hover:scale-110">
                </div>
                <div class="p-6">
                    <div class="flex items-center justify-between mb-3">
                        <span class="px-3 py-1 bg-blue-100 dark:bg-blue-900 text-blue-800 dark:text-blue-300 text-xs font-semibold rounded-full">
                            Roofing
                        </span>
                    </div>
                    <h3 class="text-xl font-bold text-gray-800 dark:text-gray-100 mb-3">
                        How to Install a Metal Roof – Step-by-Step DIY Guide
                    </h3>
                    <p class="text-gray-600 dark:text-gray-300 text-sm mb-4">
                        Installing a metal roof might sound like a big job and it is. But with the right tools, guidance, and planning, many homeowners successfully tackle this project. Metal roofing offers longevity (50+ years), energy efficiency, and fire resistance. The installation process involves measuring, preparing the roof deck, installing underlayment, and securing metal panels with appropriate fasteners.
                    </p>
                    <button onclick="openModal(3)" class="inline-flex items-center text-primary-600 dark:text-primary-400 font-medium hover:text-primary-800 dark:hover:text-primary-300 text-sm cursor-pointer">
                        Read Guide <i class="ri-arrow-right-line ml-2"></i>
                    </button>
                </div>
